nce wealthy families and demanding institutions need to have the heaviest possible firepower sitting on their side of the table at cobalt capital we assign to client accounts only senior managing directors who are at the very top of their profession making our experience count the most crucial issues such as asset allocation and manager selection are handled by cobalt capital’s managing directors not by young analysts intellectual leadership since our only stockintrade is our intellectual capital it is important that cobalt capital represent the cutting edge in every area that will have an important effect on the growth of our clients’ wealth we happily share our knowledge with investors primarily via our monthly capital markets reports and our series of cobalt capital white papers centralized knowledge base at most firms a client receives only the benefit of the knowledge the specific consultant has at cobalt capital the firm’s knowledge base is centralized and is available to all consultants and by extension to all of our clients performance reporting and monitoring cobalt capital reports are the best in the industry they are not only accurate and timely but in addition we put our clients’ results in perspective telling them in plain english how their portfolios have performed and whether there are issues that should be dealt with during that period organizational stability cobalt capital has a senior management team whose sole job it is to run the company like a business for our clients this translates into minimal personnel turnover seamless account servicing and the assurance that cobalt capital will be around to advise their grandchildren home services investing venture capital new economy special situations news contact us company address  nihonbashimuromachi chuoku tokyo ‎ japan ‎   infocobaltcapitalinccom scroll to top team  cobalt capital inc cobalt capital inc home about overview team portfolio contact team ben schick ben schick is the founder and preside